Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.49,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(420,0)\move(57,240,11,240,25,2444)}晉級準決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,貓田選手獲勝
